Future cop Jack Deth (Tim Thomerson) takes on his most thrilling adventure in this final installment of the Trancers series!
Trancers 5: Sudden Deth finds Jack trapped in the mythical land of Orpheus, where black magic abounds and deadly Trancers rule. After leading a revolt against the Trancers and killing their leader Lord Caliban, Deth still isn't any closer to finding a way back home. He's got only one hope: the Timeond, a centuries-old talisman capable of opening a dimensional vortex to any time and place.
But in order to capture the Timeond, he's going to have to wage one final battle--a fight to the death with an old foe who's come back to life...Caliban!
I have the whole series now so I am very happy.
This really is a great series of movies and Jack Deth is always up to handle the situation. He is always making wisecracks about other people or the situation he is in.
